{"tid":228771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"毒撚總係以為自己係好男人","createTime":"2017-05-04T06:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T18:24:41.000Z","uid":431,"like":141,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80ded49c646247325c5cf259d97cbe9485eae81d","tid":228771,"uid":431,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:49:29.000Z","msg":"如果悶、唔出街玩、無情趣都叫好男人嘅特徵嘅話，咁不如揀個牧師、神父、或者和尚做男朋友，起碼人地對上帝，佛陀都好專一，又仁慈。 <br />\n<br />\n根本，未拍過拖嘅人，就唔會直切感受到點先算係一個好男人"},{"pid":"540d46894eed92a653268c2336227a8e5cf1df0a","tid":228771,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:51:08.000Z","msg":"咁點先算好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00865a2a98011408d6df90b88a9cb80d30450da3","tid":228771,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"接受到 怨婦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de135c210d9fcc744b70e519182a51c779a9a40","tid":228771,"uid":6136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"一齊定義下點先係好男人<br />\n1.有錢"},{"pid":"6c144b297e8880cf2f710e44ad54c76eb46b0cf1","tid":228771,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁點先算好男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問我問邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351c25265ebf9bdab2630e020a66a2975d508c35","tid":228771,"uid":431,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:56:01.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解咁多連登仔成日話自己係好男人<br />\n雖然無工返無收入但夠專一長情<br />\n講真　有時睇到依啲ｐｏｓｔ真係眼都突埋。。。<br />\n好人好姐有手有腳　搵份工真係咁難？<br />\n搵唔到都未必係佢嘅錯 <br />\n但佢嘅心態真係好有問題 <br />\n成日覺得自己無咩缺點鍾意人人地就一定要鍾意返你<br />\n如果唔係就死港女。。。<br />\n老實講～如果係活潑開朗又善良嘅暗瘡肥婆，同港女格版林嘉欣同時追你 <br />\n你問心啦，你會揀邊個？"},{"pid":"45ca74255dd9d309f5e437a6abd14edef01f81e8","tid":228771,"uid":60455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:56:56.000Z","msg":"怨婦"},{"pid":"b59dc79269c133982c883d89545f712405ca4523","tid":228771,"uid":431,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"見到依到喺毒撚真係忍唔住屌 <br />\n成日話乜柒男不壞女不愛<br />\n成日話自己係好男人 <br />\n屌你老尾生得樣衰溝唔到女就認命啦<br />\n你班on9仔到老咗依然唔知戀愛係點處都未破啦 看破紅塵 <br />\n等我話俾D啲毒男on9仔知乜柒係好男人 <br />\n好男人係照顧到女人 <br />\n俾到個女人有安全感要保護到女人<br />\n好似個女人俾mk撩你就要企起個女人前面屌鳩個mk <br />\n唔係好似你啲毒撚咁托一托副金絲死人眼鏡同個mk仔講大佬對唔住 <br />\n屌你老尾成日話乜柒男不壞女不愛成日話自己係好男人 <br />\n好男人人唔係嗰啲日日喺屋企睇漫畫上網唔去wet唔食煙唔溝女就叫好男人囉<br />\n成日話乜柒男不壞女不愛成日話自己係好男人"},{"pid":"560e1cb44e347c53098689ce3b3bfb21d04fc201","tid":228771,"uid":828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:00:59.000Z","msg":"唔係好男人 但至少唔係壞男人"},{"pid":"bd0f8d34c153a8cb3da42c6e3377e3f8bcd958e3","tid":228771,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:02:24.000Z","msg":"好重怨氣既怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又比仔飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854d3235a25971cdfdc68ff1628fee88cf2b0843","tid":228771,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係好男人 但至少唔係壞男人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.com/albums/ah233/sorsawsor/5b17bdca_zpst9a1wmci.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1381.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F5b17bdca_zpst9a1wmci.gif&h=1781f0c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb441cad6a9fbe4dabde880844cc03a4f2b4fa99","tid":228771,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b472bbe47642022fdd1eca19515bf51512b1015f","tid":228771,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔係好男人 但至少唔係壞男人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i1381.photobucket.c